    <h1>Citation Flow</h1>
    <p class="description">A <strong>Majestic SEO metric scored 0–100</strong> that predicts URL and domain influence based on the number of sites linking in. Measures link quantity, not quality — always pair with Trust Flow.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
